3351	[Per-cover-member geometric presentation from quasi-coherence data]
3352	  \label{def:presentation_pullback_iota_of_quasicoherentData}
3353	  \lean{AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Modules.presentationPullbackιOfQuasicoherentData}
